---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Embudos de Venta | Plantilla 1">
<main>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-48 md:pb-32 bg-primary-container overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-gutter relative z-10 text-center">
<h1 class="font-display-hero-mobile md:font-display-hero text-display-hero-mobile md:text-display-hero text-on-primary mb-6">
                CONFIGURACIÓN DE EMBUDOS DE VENTA
            </h1>
<p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-primary-container/90 mb-12">
                Transforma el tráfico de tus redes sociales en un flujo constante de clientes potenciales cualificados, operando en piloto automático 24/7.
            </p>
<div class="relative w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-12 transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-700">
<img alt="Ilustración detallada de un embudo de ventas digital profesional con elementos 3D transparentes y logotipos de redes sociales integrados en un flujo de automatización moderno." class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-on-primary-container/20" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBUu9IlokmAkV3pjZ1CQete1g3cwm7HTZZMUR63uS7Icu0PC9ycgjyJm66sXVkbaO2p5gHN9vgE_647EQ8uqvdAIC9Zu2Q_xhXgNSNT2EJexJF1FZaCxnbaz0zvvb0vTedgRzTjcsZpmLVHHPjq6IQcfh5UeFPefacm08RZL5U4wjDJ41VtgwnWAwNy7P1nF3ejeLe1lN6lyCq-1cSVjVxECEvuLtnTbxJO-7Yy8qUOOMmSY_qCdEXAT-Lq4BebnNqHcsuYC5odq53g"/>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Background accents -->
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none opacity-20">
<div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-64 h-64 bg-primary-fixed rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-10 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-on-primary-container rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Pricing / Features Section -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-section-padding-mobile md:py-section-padding-desktop">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-gutter">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
<!-- Left: Dashboard Graphic -->
<div class="order-2 md:order-1">
<div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl bg-white p-4">
<img alt="Captura de pantalla de alta resolución de un panel de control de automatización de ventas con gráficos de flujo visual, métricas de conversión y una interfaz minimalista en tonos púrpura y blanco." class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDNoyfJG61Gp3ZV_HnvgRb4iHj4ozYq8xecsV5x9hiwDg7I7SeSdzfrtQ88ly52zYI7pzgWFjZb5yMKJBVlWi2pvoOBUmIkxPzTcgu2wtSP7V5TWf8cUMMIm2yyrl0_UB8vZc_i0v3gt0B9-EbGfDKpd3nShIE9VluZIO_BrnbufSihBfwRwVHt5AObmA2VNpWTkEvljXhvtfJ5BcI9mkcLpwTvQY7f_1nBRW6s4qK3bw2V1snYs8H_2RoUUtodxErC37DeJmEdYoa9"/>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Right: Pricing Card -->
<div class="order-1 md:order-2">
<div class="bg-white border-t-8 border-primary rounded-xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12 transition-all hover:shadow-2xl">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl" data-icon="star" data-weight="fill" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">star</span>
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">Automatiza tus ventas</h2>
</div>
<div class="mb-8">
<span class="text-4xl font-bold text-on-surface">$3,999</span>
<span class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md text-body-md ml-2">USD / Proyecto</span>
</div>
<ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle" data-weight="fill" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant text-left">Diseño de landing page de alta conversión</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle" data-weight="fill" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant text-left">Configuración y automatización del embudo en GoHighLevel</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle" data-weight="fill" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant text-left">Integración de calendario de citas automático</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle" data-weight="fill" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant text-left">Diseño de secuencia de 3 emails (Nurturing)</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle" data-weight="fill" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant text-left">Integración de formularios y API de conversión</span>
</li>
</ul>
<a href="/producto?service=embudos-venta&plan=automatizacion" class="w-full bg-primary-container text-on-primary font-label-sm text-label-sm py-5 rounded-lg hover:bg-opacity-90 active:scale-95 transition-all tracking-widest btn-magnetic press-effect text-center block">
                                <span class="icon-wrap">CONTRATAR AHORA</span>
                            </a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
</Layout>
